00:29:32.653 --> 00:29:34.193
Ikaw ba si Designer L?

00:29:36.163 --> 00:29:37.833
Oo, ako yun.

00:29:38.593 --> 00:29:39.593
Hello.

00:29:42.063 --> 00:29:43.133
Kang Jae In?

00:29:44.573 --> 00:29:45.803
Kilala ba kita?

00:29:47.873 --> 00:29:50.103
Naging glamorous ang istilo mo na halos hindi na kita nakilala.

00:29:50.973 --> 00:29:52.043
Ngunit ikaw ito.

00:29:52.913 --> 00:29:54.843
Sus, pasensya na.

00:29:55.083 --> 00:29:58.083
Nahihirapan akong ilagay ka.

00:30:07.653 --> 00:30:10.063
Ang tagumpay ay ang kapalaran ng mga hindi sumusuko.

00:30:10.763 --> 00:30:11.793
Best of luck.

00:30:13.463 --> 00:30:15.963
Yan ang laging sinasabi ng tatay ko.

00:30:18.833 --> 00:30:20.133
Ang LA Getty Center?

00:30:20.833 --> 00:30:21.903
Walong taon na, hindi ba?

00:30:23.673 --> 00:30:26.473
Sus, napakasaya kong makita ka.

00:30:29.483 --> 00:30:30.483
Ako si Lee Tae Oh.

00:30:33.683 --> 00:30:36.083
As in, Lee Tae Oh, ang art dealer?

00:30:37.223 --> 00:30:38.223
ako yun.

00:30:39.393 --> 00:30:41.193
To think na ang Designer L ay si Kang Jae In...

00:30:42.023 --> 00:30:43.523
Hindi ko akalain.

00:30:45.263 --> 00:30:47.563
Masasabi ko rin.

00:30:50.203 --> 00:30:51.203
Lee Tae Oh,

00:30:52.403 --> 00:30:53.803
kanina pa kita hinahanap.

00:30:56.203 --> 00:30:57.973
Kanina pa kita hinahanap, Kang Jae In.

00:31:04.243 --> 00:31:05.283
Lahat, kumusta.

00:31:05.553 --> 00:31:06.883
Ito si Lee Tae Oh, ang nagbebenta ng sining.

00:31:07.253 --> 00:31:10.083
Ito ang aming CEO, si Jung Oh Seong, at Direktor Kim Do Yun.

00:31:10.983 --> 00:31:12.023
Ikinagagalak kitang makilala.

00:31:12.453 --> 00:31:13.623
Lee Tae Oh?

00:31:15.223 --> 00:31:17.323
Maghintay, kung gayon... Kilala mo ba si Andy Rogers, kung nagkataon?

00:31:17.663 --> 00:31:19.833
Isa siyang pangunahing super-collector.

00:31:20.393 --> 00:31:21.463
Syempre.

00:31:21.733 --> 00:31:24.463
Matagal na siyang patron at special VIP ko.

00:31:25.233 --> 00:31:28.873
Ikaw ba si Patrick kung nagkataon? Iginiit ni Rogers na magkita tayo bukas.

00:31:29.273 --> 00:31:30.843
Oo, ako yun.

00:31:32.113 --> 00:31:34.213
Fancy meeting you here. Ito ay isang kasiyahan.

00:31:37.083 --> 00:31:38.213
So magkakilala na kayong dalawa?

00:31:38.613 --> 00:31:41.622
Matagal na tayong nagkita sa States,

00:31:41.623 --> 00:31:43.123
pero hindi ko alam na top art dealer pala siya.

00:31:43.653 --> 00:31:45.153
Lahat ito ay salamat kay Jae In.

