00:34:06.993 --> 00:34:08.033
salamat,

00:34:08.963 --> 00:34:09.963
Nanay.

00:34:10.333 --> 00:34:11.602
Hwang Ji-ho.

00:34:11.603 --> 00:34:13.933
Hanggang kailan mo itatago sa akin ang anak ko?

